{"tid":112293,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[週經]惠康農心公仔麵做緊特價","createTime":"2017-02-08T04:53:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T12:33:48.000Z","uid":5891,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9a736c5273080f4fb3d9a8ac88167a7ad478bee2","tid":112293,"uid":5891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T04:53:55.000Z","msg":"本身諗住去759買，點知貴到仆街，之前屋企買左包叫咩九州豬骨/咖哩嘅公仔面，難食到仆街，包湯包淡而無味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住去惠康行，見到農心嘅公仔面竟然做特價，原價$32.5 1pack (5包)，佢夠擔死賣35.8 2packs <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪話唔益你班連登仔，知道左都上嚟同你地講聲<br />\n我覺得公仔面嚟講，泡菜國嘅麵質、口感算係唔錯，我見識少，我覺得係好食過出前一丁果類<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5og8c6in\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5og8c6in&h=c4bb3934&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b78b725f299d9ef7b2e970bf6ebe6b75cdeb00a0","tid":112293,"uid":74110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T04:55:02.000Z","msg":"放學去買先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e32cd19b26179e442ee0e3fbd51b529493f3820","tid":112293,"uid":67094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T05:00:19.000Z","msg":"依家惠康啲農心全部強國造，你食埋我嗰份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n農心一定要買返泡菜國造既先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑色辛辣麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b35eecfccd450b89a620d72a48cb975c6603763c","tid":112293,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T05:00:53.000Z","msg":"狗也不<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87a1754cd7215d78e0d26c0917c2973459006293","tid":112293,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201